{"tid":668942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老係咪香港最ON9既生物","createTime":"2018-05-18T04:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T07:04:23.000Z","uid":83961,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dd751ec150cff0387797d2f1de25c1bf8c779f78","tid":668942,"uid":83961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:57:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n話說琴日我就去康文署既GYM ROOM做GYM啦<br />\n<br />\n咁我屋企附近果間呢,前排就壞左架單車機,好耐都未整好<br />\n<br />\n但係因為我都叫前排考試有成星期無去 加上前兩日係果到既器械維修日 我都諗緊會唔會整番好<br />\n<br />\n一推開門入去就見到有個呀婆用緊<br />\n<br />\n咁我以為整好啦 但我望佢去見架單車坐椅下面有條紅色既野<br />\n<br />\n我以為係個呀婆自己d野黎 無點理<br />\n<br />\n點知我熱緊身果陣 突然有個康文署職員入黎 同個呀婆講<br />\n<br />\n「呀婆，架車壞架，你唔好用啦」<br />\n<br />\n之後個呀婆話:<br />\n<br />\n「唔怪得我坐起黎怪怪地咁啦 原來係壞既」<br />\n<br />\n之後個呀婆都叫聽話落番架車<br />\n<br />\n然後佢好撚有手尾咁將 寫住維修兩隻字既紅白膠帶，幫佢纏番好<br />\n<br />\n再將掛係架車顯示器上面既維修板反番落黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n屌你老母你見到佢係壞既仲要用然後話唔怪之得坐落去唔舒服???</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9add5e2d4adc855f37f2eacb509a4154a154c2b5","tid":668942,"uid":152753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人明樓主講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79440d4916938726e612ccd57f2f31702e7c9af7","tid":668942,"uid":52178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9add5e2d4adc855f37f2eacb509a4154a154c2b5","tid":668942,"uid":152753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人明樓主講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T06:56:32.000Z","msg":"文盲?"},{"pid":"5b1b2c0d005daecfa00b10c15be42e23ec44b216","tid":668942,"uid":78885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9add5e2d4adc855f37f2eacb509a4154a154c2b5","tid":668942,"uid":152753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人明樓主講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"乖啦 夠鐘食藥啦"},{"pid":"5b2af14fddc214593a8a9bd925682b7e80701bf7","tid":668942,"uid":121754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9add5e2d4adc855f37f2eacb509a4154a154c2b5","tid":668942,"uid":152753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人明樓主講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T07:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}